" VEEFAULTS VERSION (SEE VEEFAULTS FOLDER IN THE ROOT OF THIS REPO)
" (root may be shared with others; split out the user settings to be unintrusive)

" ROOT SETTINGS
" =============
" Audiovisual :
syntax enable
set noerrorbells "no audio bell
set mat=2 "tenths of second to blink when matching brackets
" Searching :
set incsearch
set ignorecase
set smartcase
set showmatch
set hlsearch
" Other :
imap jj <ESC>

" USER SETTINGS
" =============
" Audiovisual :
set background=dark
set novisualbell
set ruler
set number "comment out if mouse select is grabbing line numbers
colorscheme desert
" Spacing :
set backspace=indent,eol,start
set expandtab
set smarttab
set shiftwidth=4
set tabstop=4
set ai
set si
" Other :
set nobackup
set nowb
set noswapfile
cmap boo w !sudo tee >/dev/null % "use L (Load) not O (Ok)
